high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the counter, then hang a left and walk up to the wall, turn right and walk over to the counter.
Open the rightmost cabinet door below the left sink and take out the bottle of lotion, then close the cabinet door.
Look up at the counter.
Put the bottle of lotion on the front edge of the counter in between the two sinks.
Turn right and walk towards the door, then hang a right and walk around the toilet.
Pick up the bottle of lotion off of the toilet tank.
Turn right and walk towards the shower, then turn left and walk over to the leftmost sink.
Put the bottle of lotion on the counter behind the bar of soap in between the two sinks.
anns.task_desc: Move two bottles of lotion to the counter.

high_descs: Turn to the left and head to the vanity in front of the left sink.
Open the right cabinet door under the left sink and take out a bottle of soap.
Take a step closer to the vanity.
Set the bottle of soap down in front of the pink bar of soap on the vanity between the two sinks.
Turn around and move to the toilet.
Pick up the bottle of soap from the back of the toilet.
Move back to the vanity.
Set the bottle of soap down behind the pink bar of soap between the two sinks.
anns.task_desc: Put two bottle of soap on the bathroom vanity between the two sinks.

high_descs: Turn left, walk towards the sink, turn left towards the wall, and then turn right to face the other sink.
Look for the right cabinet below the sink.
Open the right cabinet below the sink and take out a bottle inside it.
Place the bottle on the counter in front of the bar soap.
Turn around and head towards the toilet.
Pick up the bottle on the toilet basin.
Turn around towards the left sink.
Place the bottle behind the bar soap on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Place two bottles on the counter.
